[32m+[m[32m      <h3>Plastic-Free Pioneers</h3>[m
[32m+[m[32m      <p><strong>Ethique</strong> has eliminated plastic packaging entirely through their solid beauty bar format for everything from shampoo and conditioner to face cleansers and body lotions. Founded by biochemist Brianne West, the New Zealand-based brand has prevented more than 20 million plastic bottles from being manufactured and disposed of since its inception.</p>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m      <p>"Liquid products are primarily water, which you already have in your shower," explains West. "By removing water from formulations, we create concentrated products that require no plastic packaging and are more efficient to ship."</p>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m      <p>Their compostable packaging breaks down completely, leaving no trace in the environment. The company is also certified carbon-neutral and donates 2% of revenue to environmental charities.</p>[m
