[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m      <p>"The refill system reduces packaging waste by up to 70% compared to buying new products each time," notes sustainable packaging expert James Chen. "Kjaer Weis demonstrated that refillable systems can work even for premium beauty products without compromising the luxury experience."</p>[m
